  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-5" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">Skills and experience</h2>
  
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3">Buyers will use the essential and nice-to-have skills and experience to help them evaluate suppliers’ technical competence.</p>
  
  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Essential skills and experience
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Microsoft Certified training partners/developers</li>
          <li>Demonstrate 2 project successes in providing support for an EDRMS solution through SharePoint</li>
          <li>Provide evidence of experience in delivering flexible training for SharePoint Online and Microsoft Office 365, bespoke to clients needs</li>
          <li>Provide evidence of successful document management solutions, including search and retrieval, in SharePoint Online.</li>
          <li>Provide examples of previous successes in training staff on SharePoint Governance and architecture</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Nice-to-have skills and experience
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Have experience of working with public authorities</li>
          <li>Have experience of digital transformation</li>
          <li>Provide evidence of developing SharePoint document libraries for efficient tagging</li>
          <li>Provide evidence of delivering successful training partnership</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>

  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-6" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">How suppliers will be evaluated</h2>
  
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3">All suppliers will be asked to provide a written proposal.</p>
  
  

  

  

  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          How many suppliers to evaluate
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          3
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Proposal criteria
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Demonstrate skills, experience and previous successes in similar projects.</li>
          <li>Outline how value for money will be achieved</li>
          <li>Evidence provided which matches NILGOSC&#39;s training and development support needs</li>
          <li>How examples provided showcase solutions which the project goals.</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Cultural fit criteria
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Work as part of the Project team</li>
          <li>Work with clients with a range of technical skills</li>
          <li>Share knowledge and experience with project team members</li>
          <li>Be flexible and honour commitments</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Payment approach
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Fixed price
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Additional assessment methods
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Evaluation weighting
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-0 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Technical competence</p>
        <div>60%</div>
        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Cultural fit</p>
        <div>10%</div>
        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Price</p>
        <div>30%</div>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>

  </div>
</div>
<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-full">
    

<h2 id="clarification-questions" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">Questions asked by suppliers</h2>



  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          1. We have a document and EDRMS product that sits on SharePoint Online and integrates with other Office 365 workloads. It is very configurable and flexible and is typically used by our customers to implement ISO level controls on their documentation.<br>Using our product would provide a big head start to meeting your requirements and the flexibility and configurability in our product all comes from SharePoint and Power Platform configuration so we would still train your staff in SharePoint configuration but they would have large parts of the work already delivered. <br>Would this approach be of interest?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          NILGOSC is seeking suitably qualified and experienced suppliers to provide training and development support for a SharePoint EDRMS Solution.  The focus of the project is for the supplier to provide training on specific areas of SharePoint Online.  NILGOSC does not require any additional product at this time.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          2. Please can you confirm if this is 20 working days over a 6 month period. Or potentially a full 6 month role with 20 specific delivery / training days onsite in NI?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          NILGOSC has budget approval for 20 days at a maximum daily rate of £650 + VAT to cover training and development requirements which is expected to last approximately 6 months. We anticipate that the majority of the requirement will be delivered as onsite training but that some development work may be carried out remotely.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          3. You state that you require training to be delivered on site. As we have been successfully delivering remote training during the pandemic, is it possible that we can use this model to make the budget viable? Alternatively, is there flexibility in the day rate to make it exclusive of expenses?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          NILGOSC has secured appropriate budget approval for this project, and expect onsite attendance for training and workshop sessions, however, some development work may be carried out remotely.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>



  <p class="govuk-body">The deadline for asking questions about this opportunity was Friday 10 September 2021.</p>

  </div>
